        "svg": "<svg viewBox=\"0 0 180 90\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <rect x=\"10\" y=\"44\" width=\"160\" height=\"4\" fill=\"#3e2723\"/>\n  <polyline fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#fdd835\" stroke-width=\"6\" points=\"28,44 42,24 56,64 70,24 84,64 98,24 112,64 126,24 140,64 154,24 168,44\"/>\n  <line x1=\"4\" y1=\"44\" x2=\"28\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#b0bec5\" stroke-width=\"6\"/>\n  <line x1=\"168\" y1=\"44\" x2=\"176\" y2=\"44\" stroke=\"#b0bec5\" stroke-width=\"6\"/>\n  <text x=\"90\" y=\"80\" fill=\"#ffffff\" font-size=\"14\" font-family=\"monospace\" text-anchor=\"middle\">220Ω</text>\n</svg>",
        "memo": "Limits current before the LED. Components define their own pins so wiring stays flexible."
