    {
      "id": "node-breadboard-notes",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Breadboard Guide",
      "position": {
        "x": 759,
        "y": 146
      },
      "width": 260,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## SVG Breadboard Demo\n- Drag the switch and watch the LED path highlight on the SVG grid.\n- The logic probe monitors the LED’s cathode so you can capture when the slide switch pulls the rail to ground.\n- Every component node stores its own pin ports so the wiring feels like a real breadboard netlist.\n",
        "_classBinding": {
